import { Tabs, TabList, TabPanels, Tab, TabPanel } from '@chakra-ui/react'
import { Box, Flex, Heading, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import { CashierLogin } from '../components/cashier/cashierLogin'

export const Login = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Flex w={"full"} h={"648px"} bg={"#FFC900"} justifyContent={"center"}>
                <Box mt={"75px"} bg={"white"} w={"600px"} h={"500px"} border={"2px solid"} borderColor={"black"} borderRadius={"10px"} boxShadow={"0px 0px 10px black"} justifyContent={"center"}>
                    <Flex justifyContent={"center"}>
                        <Heading mt={"40px"} color={"#D5AD18"} fontSize={"60px"} fontFamily={"Times New Roman"}>LOGIN</Heading>
                    </Flex>

                    <Flex mt={"40px"} fontSize={"12px"} justifyContent={"center"}  >
                        <Text display={"flex"}>You have to Login to accsess this app!</Text>
                    </Flex>
                    <Flex mt={"20px"} fontSize={"20px"} color={"#D5AD18"} justifyContent={"center"} >
                        <Text display={"flex"} fontFamily={"Times New Roman"}>Login As</Text>
                    </Flex>
                    <Tabs mt={"10px"} align={"center"} variant="unstyled">
                        <TabList>
                            <Tab fontFamily={"Times New Roman"}>Cashier</Tab>
                            <Text color={"#D5AD18"} mt={"7px"}>or</Text>
                            <Tab fontFamily={"Times New Roman"}>Admin</Tab>
                        </TabList>
                        <TabPanels>
                            <TabPanel>
                                <CashierLogin />
                            </TabPanel>
                            <TabPanel>
                                
                            </TabPanel>
                        </TabPanels>
                    </Tabs>

                </Box>

            </Flex>
        </>
    )
}
